---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Marketing Company Edinburgh" description="Privacy policy for Marketing Company Edinburgh. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in accordance with UK GDPR.">
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#FAFAFA]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#0A192F] tracking-tight mb-6">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium text-xs mb-16">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })}
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Marketing Company Edinburgh is a digital marketing agency based in Edinburgh, Scotland. 
            We specialise in local SEO, PPC management, web design, and data-driven growth strategies. 
            Our registered address is Unit 2B, Eastfield Industrial Estate, Penicuik, Midlothian, EH26 8HA.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We may collect and process the following personal data:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Name and contact details (email address, phone number)</li>
            <li>Business name, website URL, and marketing requirements</li>
            <li>Information you provide via our contact forms or email correspondence</li>
            <li>Technical data such as IP address and browser type through cookies</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">How We Use Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We use cookies to improve your browsing experience and to understand how visitors interact with our website. 
            Cookies help us analyse traffic, remember your preferences, and enhance site functionality. 
            You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings at any time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use your personal data to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Respond to enquiries and provide marketing consultations</li>
            <li>Plan and deliver digital marketing services</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your project</li>
            <li>Send our "Edinburgh Marketing Insights" newsletter if you have opted in</li>
            <li>Improve our website and services</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected, 
            including for the purposes of satisfying any legal, accounting, or reporting requirements. 
            Typically, we retain client data for up to 7 years after our last interaction.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
            <li>Request erasure of your personal data (&ldquo;right to be forgotten&rdquo;)</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
            <li>Request data portability</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-[#0A192F] mb-4 tracking-tight">Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please contact us:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <p><strong>Marketing Company Edinburgh</strong></p>
            <p>Unit 2B, Eastfield Industrial Estate, Penicuik, Midlothian, EH26 8HA</p>
            <p>Phone: 0131 555 0000</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@marketing-company.co.uk" class="text-[#6B4C9A] hover:underline">info@marketing-company.co.uk</a></p>
          </address>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
